title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Mo Bamba No. 5 Pt. II with Jonah Weiner
description:
Your mission, should you choose to accept it, continues beyond the paywall as Throwing Fits continues what is already being called an “instant classic” pod with celeb whisperer and newsletter hero Jonah Weiner. Recon don’t stop, so strap into the Blackbird Spyplane with Jonah and the boys because we’re gathering intelligence on being “The Other Jonah”, blogging in 2020, chilling at Drake’s infamous Yolo Estate, shopping with A$AP Rocky, La Flame saving his life, Sean Parker slipping through his fingers, cooking up his dream profile, working for yourself and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
